WEBVTT

00:00:10.739 --> 00:00:20.374 line:90% position:50% align:center
Sarah and Esther,
Mary, Ruth, and others—

00:00:20.374 --> 00:00:28.382 line:90% position:50% align:center
All these were capable women,
loyal wives.

00:00:30.009 --> 00:00:38.517 line:90% position:50% align:center
Godly devotion was foremost
in their lives.

00:00:38.517 --> 00:00:46.150 line:90% position:50% align:center
They were faithful women,
ones we know by name.

00:00:48.193 --> 00:00:53.449 line:90% position:50% align:center
There were others
favored by Jehovah;

00:00:53.449 --> 00:01:01.498 line:90% position:50% align:center
Nameless in the record,
their faith was just the same.

00:01:07.713 --> 00:01:16.972 line:90% position:50% align:center
Goodness and courage,
loyal love and kindness—

00:01:16.972 --> 00:01:25.981 line:90% position:50% align:center
Lovable qualities
in all humankind,

00:01:25.981 --> 00:01:34.198 line:90% position:50% align:center
Virtues these excellent women
bring to mind.

00:01:34.198 --> 00:01:43.207 line:90% position:50% align:center
They were fine examples
we appreciate.

00:01:43.207 --> 00:01:48.253 line:90% position:50% align:center
In the same way now
our Christian sisters

00:01:48.253 --> 00:01:56.303 line:90% position:50% align:center
Show a faithful spirit
we all can imitate.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:12.486 line:90% position:50% align:center
Mothers and daughters,
sisters, wives, and widows,

00:02:12.486 --> 00:02:21.078 line:90% position:50% align:center
Willingly laboring,
glad to do your part.

00:02:21.078 --> 00:02:30.045 line:90% position:50% align:center
Modest your bearing,
submissive is your heart,

00:02:30.045 --> 00:02:37.428 line:90% position:50% align:center
Having God’s approval,
may you never fear.

00:02:38.679 --> 00:02:43.767 line:90% position:50% align:center
Christian sisters,
may Jehovah keep you

00:02:43.767 --> 00:02:53.027 line:90% position:50% align:center
Firm in your conviction,
your prize is drawing near.

